{"tid":1668210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪冇不反 就唔會再有百萬遊行?","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T01:55:33.000Z","uid":249705,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f85977d003ca58791c61daa42dd2f0b56220345c","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:07:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地遲早需要再有大型遊行</span><br />\n<br />\n而不得不承認<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇不反對通知書</span>+<span style=\"color: red;\">封鐵</span><br />\n就好難聚到過百萬人<br />\n一係因為有部份和理非怕法律責任<br />\n二係有啲係一家大細咁出 唔可以冒險<br />\n<br />\n但兩樣都係對家控制 可以點拆?<br />\n場運動可以點繼續?"},{"pid":"374fd167c79bedaf7cb8d6811894b3b30b4ab73c","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:09:27.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"93edbc48056ed4ae48b86ff65b711867198b9077","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:09:38.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"0d3913b70267612c1e9e80e3e21228e91e10288d","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15801f918aa4b48958c85f66d661e0b3523dbac7","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f44928015271bcacdd099e22a860310d4568d5f","tid":1668210,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"28c21742f5b9f8da1d30262efeeb5dd6510cfb88","tid":1668210,"uid":308414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"另外一個問題就係班狗而家會提早開波<br />\n冇時間聚人"},{"pid":"306d039bbf5a081fe87b27319b0481c79f0efab7","tid":1668210,"uid":80763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔係冇不反而唔出黎<br />\n係交通問題<br />\n冇黨鐵真係好難有過百萬人<br />\n1架巴士頂盡300人<br />\n好難係一個繁忙地方容納過5000部巴士<br />\n好多時隊頭行到一半 但係仲有好多人塞緊車黎唔到"},{